---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Statecraft Systems">
  <div class="manifesto-header">
    <div class="meta-row">
      <div class="meta-cell">ENTITY: STATECRAFT SYSTEMS</div>
      <div class="meta-cell text-center">FOCUS: STRUCTURES OF PERSISTENCE</div>
      <div class="meta-cell text-right">OP-TRADITION / 01</div>
    </div>
    <h1 class="canonical-statement">Good rule is the foundation of all human flourishing, and it endures only through structures worthy of it.</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="dossier-grid">
    <!-- Section I -->
    <div class="dossier-row">
      <div class="dossier-label">
        <span class="num">I</span>
        <span class="title">The Situation</span>
      </div>
      <div class="dossier-content long-form">
        <p>AI has restructured the operative environment. Every workflow, role, and form of cooperation is being reorganized.</p>
        <p>The distinction between AI-native and AI-naive is a distinction in sovereignty. Meanwhile, the structures built for the twentieth century cannot withstand what is happening now.</p>
        <div class="highlight-block">The technological transformation and the structural crisis are the same event.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section II -->
    <div class="dossier-row">
      <div class="dossier-label">
        <span class="num">II</span>
        <span class="title">What We Do</span>
      </div>
      <div class="dossier-content">
        <div class="capability-split">
          <div class="cap-col">
            <div class="cap-header">Technical Capacity</div>
            <p class="long-form">We make people AI-native by building real tools on real workflows, on their devices, with their challenges. Not training. Not consulting. Formation through direct work.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cap-col">
            <div class="cap-header">Structural Capacity</div>
            <p class="long-form">We help people see the structures they are in, understand why those structures produce the results they produce, and build new ones that advance toward what they want.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="dossier-note mt-lg">
          Structural tension is established. Current reality is assessed. The path forward is designed and built.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section III -->
    <div class="dossier-row">
      <div class="dossier-label">
        <span class="num">III</span>
        <span class="title">Engagement</span>
      </div>
      <div class="dossier-content">
        <div class="path-table">
          <div class="path-col">
            <div class="path-target">Individual Track</div>
            <div class="path-notes">Personal capability first.</div>
            <div class="sequence">
              <div class="seq-step"><span class="seq-name">Entry</span><span class="seq-meta">~3hrs</span></div>
              <div class="seq-step"><span class="seq-name">Infrastructure</span><span class="seq-meta">2wks</span></div>
              <div class="seq-step"><span class="seq-name">Spar</span><span class="seq-meta">Monthly</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="path-col">
            <div class="path-target">Team Track</div>
            <div class="path-notes">Systematic implementation.</div>
            <div class="sequence">
              <div class="seq-step"><span class="seq-name">Survey</span><span class="seq-meta">Assess</span></div>
              <div class="seq-step"><span class="seq-name">Construction</span><span class="seq-meta">Build</span></div>
              <div class="seq-step"><span class="seq-name">Drill</span><span class="seq-meta">Form</span></div>
              <div class="seq-step"><span class="seq-name">Continuity</span><span class="seq-meta">Maintain</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/services" class="production-link mt-lg">View Service Details</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section IV -->
    <div class="dossier-row">
      <div class="dossier-label">
        <span class="num">IV</span>
        <span class="title">Alignment</span>
      </div>
      <div class="dossier-content long-form">
        <p><strong>This work is for:</strong> Decision-makers willing to do the work. People who will build, have hard conversations about what is real, and commit to advance rather than cosmetic change.</p>
        <p><strong>It is not for:</strong> Those who want to automate without understanding, treat transformation as procurement, or seek to extract without reciprocating.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section V -->
    <div class="dossier-row border-bottom-0">
      <div class="dossier-label">
        <span class="num">V</span>
        <span class="title">The Web</span>
      </div>
      <div class="dossier-content">
        <p class="long-form mb-0">What we are building is young, but it has the structure of persistence: content, practice, transmission, community, and the institutions to carry it forward. An operative tradition.</p>
        <div class="manifesto-links">
          <a href="https://modernminuteman.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Modern Minuteman</a>
          <span class="sep">/</span>
          <a href="https://fieldcompany.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Field Company</a>
          <span class="sep">/</span>
          <a href="/work">Productions</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
